Class DeviceResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • manito.eft.interfaces.DeviceResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable
    public class DeviceResponse
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    Entity class for holding details of a device proxy response made (in either direction) between POS and terminal/core.
